#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1418
msgid "Important Note"
msgstr "Nota Importante"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:778
msgid "Enable Advanced Credit/Debit Card"
msgstr "Habilitar tarjeta de crédito/débito avanzada"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:780
msgid ""
"Enable the Advanced Credit/Debit Card payment option as a separate gateway "
"on the checkout page. This gateway typically offers a lower PayPal fee "
"compared to the PayPal Smart Button. The fee is 2.59% + $0.49* per "
"transaction for Advanced Credit/Debit Card payments and 3.49% + $0.49* for "
"PayPal Smart Buttons. It supports major cards like Visa, Mastercard, and "
"American Express, providing a secure and streamlined payment experience."
msgstr ""
"Habilita la opción de pago con tarjeta de crédito/débito avanzada como una "
"pasarela separada en la página de pago. Esta pasarela generalmente ofrece "
"una tarifa de PayPal más baja en comparación con el botón inteligente de "
"PayPal. La tarifa es del 2.59% + $0.49* por transacción para pagos con "
"tarjeta de crédito/débito avanzada y del 3.49% + $0.49* para botones "
"inteligentes de PayPal. Soporta las principales tarjetas como Visa, "
"Mastercard y American Express, proporcionando una experiencia de pago segura"
" y simplificada."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:786
msgid ""
"Set the title for the Advanced Credit/Debit Card payment method as it will "
"appear on the checkout page (e.g., 'Pay with Credit/Debit Card').."
msgstr ""
"Establece el título para el método de pago con tarjeta de crédito/débito "
"avanzado como aparecerá en la página de pago (por ejemplo, 'Pagar con "
"tarjeta de crédito/débito')."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:787
#: ppcp/includes/ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-function.php:1112
msgid "Credit or Debit Card"
msgstr "Tarjeta de Crédito o Débito"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:791
msgid "Disable specific credit cards"
msgstr "Deshabilitar tarjetas de crédito específicas"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:797
msgid ""
"By default all possible credit cards will be accepted. You can disable some "
"cards, if you wish."
msgstr ""
"Por defecto, se aceptarán todas las tarjetas de crédito posibles. Puedes "
"desactivar algunas tarjetas, si lo deseas."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:804
msgid "Contingency for 3D Secure"
msgstr "Contingencia para 3D Secure"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:808
msgid "3D Secure when required"
msgstr "3D Secure cuando sea necesario"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:809
msgid "Always trigger 3D Secure"
msgstr "Siempre activar 3D Secure"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:813
msgid ""
"3D Secure benefits cardholders and merchants by providing an additional "
"layer of verification using Verified by Visa, MasterCard SecureCode and "
"American Express SafeKey."
msgstr ""
"3D Secure beneficia a los titulares de tarjetas y a los comerciantes al "
"proporcionar una capa adicional de verificación utilizando Verified by Visa,"
" MasterCard SecureCode y American Express SafeKey."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:816
msgid "Card Save Enabled"
msgstr "Guardado de tarjeta habilitado"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:817
msgid "Enable card saving at checkout"
msgstr "Habilitar el guardado de tarjetas en el proceso de pago"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:820
msgid ""
"When enabled, customers can securely save their card details using PayPal "
"for faster future checkouts."
msgstr ""
"Cuando está habilitado, los clientes pueden guardar de forma segura los "
"detalles de su tarjeta utilizando PayPal para realizar pagos más rápidos en "
"el futuro."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:831
msgid ""
"Advanced Credit/Debit Card payments are not enabled in your PayPal account. "
"<br><br><strong>Supported Countries:</strong><br>Australia, Austria, "
